    <title>高德地图——让 Marker 在规划好的路线上平滑移动</title>
    <link href="http://blog.yuegs.com/2018/04/22/%E9%AB%98%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E8%AE%A9%20Marker%20%E5%9C%A8%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8A%E5%B9%B3%E6%BB%91%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8/"/>
    <id>http://blog.yuegs.com/2018/04/22/高德地图——让 Marker 在规划好的路线上平滑移动/</id>
    <published>2018-04-22T03:14:53.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-04-22T03:20:47.210Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&emsp;Marker，即地图上的覆盖物；规划好的路线，即在若干关键点之间进行路径规划（步行、骑行、驾车）；平滑移动，即按照一定速度移动，并且可以动态实时调整 Marker 的移动速度。<br>&emsp;对于 marker 来说，本质上就是动态在界面上添加一个 View，所以这里需要注意的是，添加的顺序会导致不同 marker 的遮挡问题。所谓规划好的路线，实际上就是一条折线。而这个折线，是其先在路线上采点，然后用直线连接相连两个点之后形成的。那就是如果对于 A 点 和 B 点之间，物理上原本就是一条直线，那么它采点可能就是稀疏的，而如果 A 和 B 之间是一条弯弯曲曲的路径，为了能更好的描述这个细节，这段路径上采点可能就会密集。相邻两个点之间，就是一个 Step，可以封装这段路程之间的距离、需要走多长时间等信息。平滑移动，运行着的是一个动画。我们都知道，动画是一帧一帧的，本质上来讲，其实就是我们在极短的时间里不断改变 marker 的位置，就形成了移动。速度的改变，其实就是调节这段时间内，marker 位置变化的程度。</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="通过-RouteSearch-获取-Point"><a href="#通过-RouteSearch-获取-Point" class="headerlink" title="通过 RouteSearch 获取 Point"></a>通过 RouteSearch 获取 Point</h3><p>&emsp;上面已经说过，规划的路径，本质上的展现形式是一些列的点的连线，即，一条折线。现在我们首先要解决的就是这些点的获取问题。<br>&emsp;RouteSearch 可以帮助我们解决这个问题。根据官网的说法:</p><blockquote><p>该类路径规划搜索的入口，定义此类开始路径规划搜索</p></blockquote><p>&emsp;我们可以使用该类进行路径的规划。一般情况，我们会使用三种模式：步行、骑行、驾车三种模式的规划选择。我使用的步行模式。但是在这种模式下，是支持多点规划的，即设置好若干要经过的关键点，然后规划出一条路线。它能够做的就是在唯一起点和唯一之间规划。不过这个问题也好解决，那就是我们多调用几次规划方法，将每次的结果存起来，这个结果，就是后续在地图上画路径的基础。<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mRouteSearch = new RouteSearch(mContext);</span><br><span class="line">mRouteSearch.setRouteSearchListener(new RouteSearch.OnRouteSearchListener() &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">@Override</span><br><span class="line">public void onBusRouteSearched(BusRouteResult busRouteResult, int i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">@Override</span><br><span class="line">public void onDriveRouteSearched(DriveRouteResult driveRouteResult, int i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">@Override</span><br><span class="line">public void onWalkRouteSearched(WalkRouteResult walkRouteResult, int i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">//如果结果为 null，则路线规划失败，可以选择立即重新规划、等待几秒后重新规划或者放弃本路段的规划</span><br><span class="line">if (walkRouteResult == null) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">searchRoute();</span><br><span class="line">return;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">// walkMultiRouteOverlay 是对路线显示的封装，这个类，是我对官网Demo中的 walkRouteOverlay 改造而成的，主要是改变了能够多次 addPath 的方法。</span><br><span class="line">if (walkMultiRouteOverlay == null) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">walkMultiRouteOverlay = new WalkMultiRouteOverlay(mContext, aMap, startPoint, endPoint,currentPoint);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">//从规划的结果中，取出路线，这里的 Path</span><br><span class="line">final WalkPath walkPath = walkRouteResult.getPaths().get(0);</span><br><span class="line">//将返回的结果 Path 存放到 walkMultiRouteOverlay 中，以便作为后期显示的数据源</span><br><span class="line">walkMultiRouteOverlay.addPath(walkPath);</span><br><span class="line">//如所有规划段都完成，则可以使用 walkMultiRouteOverlay 将数据源构成的折线显示在地图上，然后开始移动</span><br><span class="line">if (counter == maxRouteIndex) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">walkMultiRouteOverlay.addToMap();</span><br><span class="line">walkMultiRouteOverlay.zoomToSpan();</span><br><span class="line">            //注意，这里所有路径就已经规划完了， marker 就可以平滑移动了</span><br><span class="line">startMove();</span><br><span class="line">zoomTo(18);</span><br><span class="line">return;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">//如果还没有规划好所有的路线</span><br><span class="line">if (counter &lt; maxRouteIndex) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">//此时，继续规划下面相邻点的路线</span><br><span class="line">searchRoute();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">@Override</span><br><span class="line">public void onRideRouteSearched(RideRouteResult rideRouteResult, int i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">//开始规划路线</span><br><span class="line">searchRoute();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>&emsp;searchRoute 方法：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">private void searchRoute() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    RoutePoint currentRoutePoint = routeManager.getKeyRoutePoints()[counter];</span><br><span class="line">    RoutePoint nextRoutePoint = routeManager.getKeyRoutePoints()[++counter];</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    LatLonPoint mStartPoint = new LatLonPoint(currentRoutePoint.getLatitude().doubleValue(),currentRoutePoint.getLongitude().doubleValue()); </span><br><span class="line">    LatLonPoint mEndPoint = new LatLonPoint(nextRoutePoint.getLatitude().doubleValue(), nextRoutePoint.getLongitude().doubleValue()); </span><br><span class="line">    final RouteSearch.FromAndTo fromAndTo = new RouteSearch.FromAndTo(mStartPoint, mEndPoint);</span><br><span class="line">RouteSearch.WalkRouteQuery query = new RouteSearch.WalkRouteQuery(fromAndTo);</span><br><span class="line">    mRouteSearch.calculateWalkRouteAsyn(query);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>&emsp;而 addToMap 方法实际上是将这条由相邻点构成的折线添加在地图上：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public void addToMap()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">initPolylineOptions();</span><br><span class="line">mPolylineOptions.add(startPoint);</span><br><span class="line">try &#123;</span><br><span class="line">for (int i = 0; i &lt; walkPaths.size(); i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">WalkStep rideStep = walkPaths.get(i);</span><br><span class="line">addRidePolyLines(rideStep);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">mPolylineOptions.add(endPoint);</span><br><span class="line">addStartAndEndMarker();</span><br><span class="line">//    addCurrentPositionMaker() ;</span><br><span class="line">showPolyline();</span><br><span class="line">&#125; catch (Throwable e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">e.printStackTrace();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="更多自定义样式"><a href="#更多自定义样式" class="headerlink" title="更多自定义样式"></a>更多自定义样式</h3><p>&emsp;在规划好的路径-折线上，体现更多细节：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PolylineOptions mPolylineOptions;</span><br><span class="line">mPolylineOptions.setCustomTexture(BitmapDescriptorFactory.fromResource(R.drawable.road_line)).width(getRouteWidth()) ;</span><br><span class="line">Polyline polyline = mAMap.addPolyline(options);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>&emsp;设置 UI :<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">aMap.setOnMapTouchListener(motionEvent -&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">return;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">aMap.showBuildings(true);</span><br><span class="line">aMap.showMapText(true);</span><br><span class="line">//关闭拥以颜色显示挤路线</span><br><span class="line">aMap.setTrafficEnabled(false);</span><br><span class="line">aMap.setMapType(AMap.MAP_TYPE_NAVI);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">aMap.setMapCustomEnable(true);//true 开启; false 关闭</span><br><span class="line">UiSettings uiSettings = aMap.getUiSettings();</span><br><span class="line">uiSettings.setAllGesturesEnabled(false);</span><br><span class="line">uiSettings.setCompassEnabled(false);</span><br><span class="line">uiSettings.setScaleControlsEnabled(false);</span><br><span class="line">uiSettings.setIndoorSwitchEnabled(false);</span><br><span class="line">uiSettings.setZoomControlsEnabled(false);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>&emsp;自定义地图样式,这是一个非常有用的功能，尤其是对于希望进行更多定制地图的需求，更多内容可以参看<a href="http://lbs.amap.com/getting-started/mapstyle" target="_blank" rel="noopener">自定义地图</a>：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">aMap.setCustomMapStylePath(&quot;/sdcard/style.data&quot;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="让-Marker-动起来"><a href="#让-Marker-动起来" class="headerlink" title="让 Marker 动起来"></a>让 Marker 动起来</h3><p>&emsp;上面，我们已经获取了数据源。现在，再看一下如何让 marker 数据源上平滑的移动起来。其实地图的 SDK 中本身提供 SmoothMoveMarker 这样的类来实现这个功能，但是，请放心，这个类通常不能满足你的需求。一下，就是 SDK 提供的 SmoothMoveMarker 关于平滑移动的秘密：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//开辟一个新的线程，执行循环，每个循环休眠 20 ms，即mStepDuration=20</span><br><span class="line">for(; !SmoothMoveMarker.this.exitFlag.get() &amp;&amp; SmoothMoveMarker.this.index &lt;= SmoothMoveMarker.this.points.size() - 1; Thread.sleep(SmoothMoveMarker.this.mStepDuration)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    synchronized(SmoothMoveMarker.this.mLock) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        if (SmoothMoveMarker.this.exitFlag.get()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            return;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        if (SmoothMoveMarker.this.STATUS != SmoothMoveMarker.a.d) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        //这里获取从开始移动至今的时长</span><br><span class="line">            long var2 = System.currentTimeMillis() - SmoothMoveMarker.this.mAnimationBeginTime;</span><br><span class="line">            //根据时长，判断当地点应处的位置</span><br><span class="line">            IPoint var6 = SmoothMoveMarker.this.getCurPosition(var2);</span><br><span class="line">            //将 marker 放置到那个位置上</span><br><span class="line">            SmoothMoveMarker.this.marker.setGeoPoint(var6);</span><br><span class="line">            SmoothMoveMarker.this.STATUS = SmoothMoveMarker.a.c;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>&emsp;首先，我们看到，它实际上是<strong>通过不停变化 marker 的位置，当移动的时间极短，就达到移动的动画效果</strong>。对于默认 SmoothMoveMarker ，调整速度的关键，是对时长的设置。事实上，它不关注这段路程到底有多长，应为在路径规划好之后，这是一个定值；也不会关注速度怎么样，唯一的调整参数就是我们设置的移动过程的时长。我们通过 getCurPosition 来进一步看，关键代码如下（注意，下面并非源代码，而是反编译之后的结果）：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// var1 就是我们传递进来的持续时间</span><br><span class="line">// 这里根据持续时间计算出 marker 已经行驶了 var3 米</span><br><span class="line">double var3 = (double)var1 * this.totalDistance / (double)this.duration;</span><br><span class="line">// 还剩余 remainDistance 米</span><br><span class="line">this.remainDistance = this.totalDistance - var3;</span><br><span class="line">int var9 = 0;</span><br><span class="line">double var5 = 1.0D;</span><br><span class="line">// 行驶了 var3 米时，marker 应当在 var9 和 var9+1 这两个点之间</span><br><span class="line">for(int var2 = 0; var2 &lt; this.eachDistance.size(); ++var2) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    double var7 = (Double)this.eachDistance.get(var2);</span><br><span class="line">    if (var3 &lt;= var7) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        if (var7 &gt; 0.0D) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">// var5 的目的，后面会用到，是为了确定 marker 在两个 point 之间的位置</span><br><span class="line">            var5 = var3 / var7;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        var9 = var2;</span><br><span class="line">        break;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    var3 -= var7;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">// move 回调，但是这个回调是不靠谱的，var9 == this.index 是很常见的事，尤其对于采点稀疏的路段，所以其被调用的时机无法掌握</span><br><span class="line">if (var9 != this.index &amp;&amp; this.moveListener != null) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    this.moveListener.move(this.remainDistance);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">this.index = var9;</span><br><span class="line">//拿到 var9 这个点的经纬度</span><br><span class="line">LatLng var11 = (LatLng)this.points.get(var9);</span><br><span class="line">//拿到 var9 下一个点的经纬度</span><br><span class="line">LatLng var16 = (LatLng)this.points.get(var9 + 1);</span><br><span class="line">IPoint var8 = new IPoint();</span><br><span class="line">// 经纬度到 GEO 的转换</span><br><span class="line">MapProjection.lonlat2Geo(var11.longitude, var11.latitude, var8);</span><br><span class="line">IPoint var10 = new IPoint();</span><br><span class="line">MapProjection.lonlat2Geo(var16.longitude, var16.latitude, var10);</span><br><span class="line">int var13 = var10.x - var8.x;</span><br><span class="line">int var4 = var10.y - var8.y;</span><br><span class="line">// 旋转 marker </span><br><span class="line">if (AMapUtils.calculateLineDistance(var11, var16) &gt; 5.0F) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">float var12 = this.getRotate(var8, var10);</span><br><span class="line">this.marker.setRotateAngle(360.0F - var12 + this.mAMap.getCameraPosition().bearing);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">// 返回 marker 的当前位置</span><br><span class="line">return new IPoint((int)((double)var8.x + (double)var13 * var5), (int)((double)var8.y + (double)var4 * var5));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>&emsp;唯一可以改变的是 marker 移动的持续时间，但是应当可以注意到，我们并不能通过更改时间来达到更改速度的目的。还记得上面那段关键代码吗？ duration 就是我们能够更改的持续时间。更改这个变量后，只会使得 marker 忽然调到一个新的位置上，然后以匀速运行。</p><h3 id="改进后的-SmoothMoveMarker"><a href="#改进后的-SmoothMoveMarker" class="headerlink" title="改进后的 SmoothMoveMarker"></a>改进后的 SmoothMoveMarker</h3><p>&emsp;下面，让我们来改进 SmoothMoveMarker，使得可以随时更改其运行速度。下面的代码是为了获取当前 marker 已经行驶的距离，并将这个距离转为了 marker 在地图上的实际显示点。距离的不断增加，且变化周期极短(20ms)，使得 marker 不断平滑前进。<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// var1 ，即从开始移动到现在的时间</span><br><span class="line">// 这里根据持续时间计算出 marker 已经行驶了 var3 米</span><br><span class="line">double var3 = (double)var1 * this.totalDistance / (double)this.duration;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>&emsp;由此可见，我们希望仅仅通过修改 duration 来平滑过渡速度已经没有意义了。 var3 的变化程度几乎完全取决于 duration 的变化程度， 因为 var1 的变化是缓慢的，每次增加 20 ms。duration 的突变，会导致 var3 的突变。<br>&emsp;在修改 duration 的时候，同时修改 已经移动的时间 var1 的计算方式，这种方案应该也可以达到平滑移动的效果。通过 var1 修正 duration 改变所带来的 marker 行驶距离的突变。<br>&emsp;另外一种方案，修改下上面那段代码，大概应该是这样的：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var 3 = var3 + speed * sliceTime ;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>&emsp;因此，你需要根据个人需求，增加一个算 speed 的方法。sliceTime 可以就设置为计算位置的一个时间循环间隔。<br>&emsp;我个人的需求相对这些要稍微复杂些，服务端 和 客户端同时规划好路线，服务端计算好这段路线的总路程，这里暂时标记为 serverTotalDistance ，那么用户在行驶了 serverTotalDistance 必将达到路线的终点。问题在于今天规划好的路线，过几天之后由于道路施工等原因，就可能发生变化。这是 serverTotalDistance 和 客户端联网计算的 clientTotalDistance 就不一致了。这个时候，肯定要以 服务器早先设置好的总路程为准。此时：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">double var3 = getUserDistance()/ distanceRate  ;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>&emsp;distanceRate，其实就是 serverTotalDistance 和 clientTotalDistance 之间的比值。 我们通过 getUserDistance 持续来获取用户实际的行驶路程，就得到了其在地图上应该所在的位置。</p><h3 id="小结"><a href="#小结" class="headerlink" title="小结"></a>小结</h3><p>&emsp;所谓路径规划的结果，不过是一条折线。跟现实类似的，如果某一段路线上，折线细节不复杂，采点就可能稀疏，否则，需要采集更多点描述这些细节。将这条折线绘制在地图上，就行程我们看到的规划路径。<br>&emsp;Marker 也是一样的，终究都逃不过一个 View。<br>&emsp;最后，需要注意的是不同版本地图 SDK 之间的 SmoothMoveMarker 实现可能是不一样的。我所使用版本的 <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yuegs/yuegs.github.io/master/file/SmoothMoveMarker.txt" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SmoothMoveMarker</a> 是这样的，可以直接拿来，做一些代码修改以完成自己的业务需求。</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;&amp;emsp;Marker，即地图上的覆盖物；规划好的路线，即在若干关键点之间进行路径规划（步行、骑行、驾车）；平滑移动，即按照一定速度移动，并且可以动态实时调整 Marker 的移动速度。&lt;br&gt;&amp;emsp;对于 marker 来说，本质上就是动态在界面上添加一个 View，所以这里需要注意的是，添加的顺序会导致不同 marker 的遮挡问题。所谓规划好的路线，实际上就是一条折线。而这个折线，是其先在路线上采点，然后用直线连接相连两个点之后形成的。那就是如果对于 A 点 和 B 点之间，物理上原本就是一条直线，那么它采点可能就是稀疏的，而如果 A 和 B 之间是一条弯弯曲曲的路径，为了能更好的描述这个细节，这段路径上采点可能就会密集。相邻两个点之间，就是一个 Step，可以封装这段路程之间的距离、需要走多长时间等信息。平滑移动，运行着的是一个动画。我们都知道，动画是一帧一帧的，本质上来讲，其实就是我们在极短的时间里不断改变 marker 的位置，就形成了移动。速度的改变，其实就是调节这段时间内，marker 位置变化的程度。&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
